print("Hello word wizards! Unleash your creativity and make up hilarious stories with Mad Libs!")

# Get input from the user
name = input("Enter a name: ")
adj1 = input("Enter an adjective: ")
adj2 = input("Enter another adjective: ")
noun1 = input("Enter a noun: ")
noun2 = input("Enter another noun: ")
animal = input("Enter an animal: ")
food = input("Enter a food: ")
verb = input("Enter a verb: ")
color = input("Enter a color: ")
instrument = input("Enter a musical instrument: ")

# Display the story
print("\nHere's your story:\n")
print(f"{name} was a {adj1} warrior who loved to play {instrument}. A long time ago, {name} went on a {adj2} journey to find the legendary {noun1}. Along the way, {name} met a friendly {animal} who offered to help. They traversed through the forest,mountains and even encountered a giant {noun2}. At last, they reached the destination and found delicious {food} waiting for them. {name} couldn't resist and {verb} it all in one bite. The whole world turned {color} and {name} felt like they were flying! From that day on, {name} became known as the {adj2} {noun1} hunter and lived happily ever after.\n")

print("Thank you for playing Mad Libs!")
